examples.en: They have names that were popular a century ago.
He is a popular guy in school.
That is a very popular misconception.
Spicy foods have become increasingly popular.
Her theories are popular among social scientists.
Vitamin C is popularly believed to prevent colds.
The President of Korea is popularly elected every five years.
The word groovy was popular in the 1960s but it's outdated now.
The nature of conscience, which I will describe as popularly as I can.
The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints is popularly known as the Mormon Church.
